snippet.title: No Matter How I Look at It, It's You Guys' Fault I'm Hiding!
snippet.description:
Download : https://blog.naver.com/plasticbag0/221648105920
If you enjoyed this game, leave a comment please.
--------------------------
The fan game of Tanigawa Nico's cartoon 'No Matter How I Look at It, It's You Guys' Fault I'm Not Popular!' 
You are one of Kuroki's friends and you want to go home with Kuroki.
If you catch Kuroki, you can see the ending cut scene

For more information, see ReadMe!.txt in the folder. 

Please enjoy it!
developer blog : https://blog.naver.com/plasticbag0
